strategies: I tried to simply rely on my own personal knowledge of cities; either I know of or have been to; and my own opinions of those names
familiar: any city I have been to is of course most familiar; but particularly cities in the US are more familiar to me; or large well known cities outside the US
memorable: cities with extremely unique names stood out more; or ones I have been too are especially memorable
unique: cities with interesting names or no similar features like Fort or ville were more unique in general
realistic: most were realistic because most were cities I had heard of before
